1. *Scena* je postavljena za predstavu. (The stage is set up for the performance.)
2. Pevač je izašao na *scenu*. (The singer came out on stage.)
3. U pozadini *scene* vidimo grad. (In the background of the scene, we see the city.)
4. Glumica je dobila nagradu za najbolju ulogu na *sceni*. (The actress received an award for the best performance on stage.)
5. Publika je bila oduševljena *scenom*. (The audience was thrilled with the scene.)
6. Poznati reditelj je kreirao *scenografiju* za pozorišnu predstavu. (A famous director created the set design for the theatrical performance.)
7. *Scenski* nastup je trajao dva sata. (The stage performance lasted two hours.)
8. Producenti su želeli da snime *scenu* u prirodi. (The producers wanted to film a scene in nature.)
9. Dramski pisac je napisao odličnu *scensku* adaptaciju romana. (The playwright wrote an excellent stage adaptation of the novel.)
10. Na *sceni* se pojavio neočekivani gost. (An unexpected guest appeared on stage.)

(Note: The word "scena" can be translated as "stage", "scene", "set", or "performance" depending on the context.)